{"tid":889037,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國頻現山寨展覽 草間彌生斥掠奪感遺憾","createTime":"2018-11-04T08:56:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-04T20:55:03.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b9405a17793e68ecee7162dc10d83b00cbe69966","tid":889037,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T08:56:47.000Z","msg":"中國上海和長沙等地自今年9月起，相繼舉辦假冒日本著名藝術家草間彌生和村上隆的展覽。草間彌生對此感到憤怒，並於周五（2日）批評這是一種掠奪，並表示無比遺憾。<br />\n草間彌生紀念藝術財團指，部分「山寨」展覽曾被叫停，但有部分可能目前正在其他城市舉辦，正調查實際情況。89歲的草間彌生親自發聲明︰「這是掠奪窮我一生的創作、以錯誤的形式被大家看到，此種情形實在令人無比遺憾。」草間彌生呼籲停止所有假展覽，希望眾人直接親眼觀賞其藝術的真正姿態。<br />\n東京草間彌生美術館館長建畠晢則表示，國際矚目前衞藝術家的偽冒作品及相關展覽，嚴重侵害藝術家的著作權，會阻礙藝術整體發展。草間彌生和村上隆的代理人正考慮向偽冒展覽的主辦單位採取法律行動。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20181103/photo/bkn-20181103112338702-1103_00912_001_01p.jpg?20181103121854\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20181103%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181103112338702-1103_00912_001_01p.jpg%3F20181103121854&h=076ddb06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20181103/photo/bkn-20181103112338702-1103_00912_001_02b.jpg?20181103121854\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20181103%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181103112338702-1103_00912_001_02b.jpg%3F20181103121854&h=59c39b6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20181103/photo/bkn-20181103112338702-1103_00912_001_03b.jpg?20181103121854\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20181103%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181103112338702-1103_00912_001_03b.jpg%3F20181103121854&h=d8e6fe4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20181103/photo/bkn-20181103112338702-1103_00912_001_04b.jpg?20181103121854\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20181103%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181103112338702-1103_00912_001_04b.jpg%3F20181103121854&h=e9fec93d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b6cdad2122a62a7c27505789a324fef31046dc0a","tid":889037,"uid":70786,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T08:59:00.000Z","msg":"支那人最喜歡掠奪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"772f71bfe8dec277ce14aef81d16631066c54f9c","tid":889037,"uid":57513,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T09:01:21.000Z","msg":"睇下班5毛會唔會講香港人都一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"756961ed281eb597cb92ff998aef5cec53ff8b64","tid":889037,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T09:09:53.000Z","msg":"咪以為咁就算呀 拍片道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e33bb79a19bfcc114bbc83128ad82b747127edd9","tid":889037,"uid":41245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"772f71bfe8dec277ce14aef81d16631066c54f9c","tid":889037,"uid":57513,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T09:01:21.000Z","msg":"睇下班5毛會唔會講香港人都一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T09:16:42.000Z","msg":"1.香港咪又係噉<br />\n2.華人DNA冇得救<br />\n3.外國人唔識分香港同中國啦，咪係抄襲大國<br />\n4.起碼人地搞藝術賺到錢，香港做藝術食屎係第三世界<br />\n仲有冇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b03ecc4f1ac1ac2fa49f6c51efb6fba8da69c850","tid":889037,"uid":57513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e33bb79a19bfcc114bbc83128ad82b747127edd9","tid":889037,"uid":41245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"772f71bfe8dec277ce14aef81d16631066c54f9c","tid":889037,"uid":57513,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T09:01:21.000Z","ms